PrecisEnactment of an ORDER PROHIBITING ENTRY ON CERTAIN LANDS IN THE YUKON TERRITORY (2000-No. 1, YUKON AIRPORT LANDS AT MINTO, PELLY CROSSING AND McQUESTEN, Y.T.) - which prohibits, until August 31, 2010, the staking of mineral claims or prospecting for precious minerals on specified tracts of land in the Yukon reserved for airport development.
